It should rather use xe_map_memset() as the BO is created with
XE_BO_FLAG_VRAM_IF_DGFX in xe_guc_pc_init().

Fixes: dd08ebf6c352 ("drm/xe: Introduce a new DRM driver for Intel GPUs")
